---
---
<section id="hero" class="hero-section">
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <img
      src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/wMWsWm7njm6vmBfMVwkVaW4.png"
      alt=""
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="hero-bg-img"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="hero-container">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Startup Weekend<br />2025 🎊</h1>
      <p>
        <strong>Du 21/11 au 23/11</strong> : L'événement pour monter un projet et vivre en accéléré
        la création d'une startup, à Nantes.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://www.billetweb.fr/startup-weekend-nantes-2025"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn-primary"
      >
        Je m'inscris maintenant
      </a>
    </div>

    <figure class="hero-image" aria-hidden="true">
      <img
        src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/oRq8HnnCP8CkxrvFeQvMp4tBA.png"
        alt="Participants au Startup Weekend"
        width="538"
        height="441"
      />
    </figure>

    <img
      src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/Zs0OyquSGNwZhNIZqYL3KdgW8Rs.svg"
      alt=""
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="hero-dots"
    />
    <img
      src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/QRQRAXnHu5ilXCmjG8WsfC9XA.svg"
      alt=""
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="hero-circle"
    />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: rgb(14, 2, 24);
    padding-top: 80px;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-bg-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    opacity: 0.15;
  }

  .hero-container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-text {
    grid-column: 1;
  }

  .hero-text h1 {
    font-family: 'Dela Gothic One', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-text p {
    font-family: 'Oxanium', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
    background: rgb(39, 168, 224);
    color: rgb(25, 5, 50);
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 0 rgb(23, 116, 156);
    transition: box-shadow 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 3px 0 rgb(23, 116, 156);
    transform: translateY(2px);
  }

  .hero-image {
    grid-column: 2;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .hero-image img {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .hero-dots {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20%;
    right: 5%;
    width: 120px;
    opacity: 0.6;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-circle {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 15%;
    left: 5%;
    width: 60px;
    opacity: 0.5;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .hero-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-text p {
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .hero-image {
      grid-column: 1;
      justify-content: center;
      order: -1;
    }

    .hero-image img {
      max-width: 280px;
    }

    .hero-dots,
    .hero-circle {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1239px) {
    .hero-container {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-text p {
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .hero-image img {
      max-width: 338px;
    }
  }
</style>
